{"tid":1530770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日被藍絲屋企人煩住嘅人可以試下呢招","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T05:15:28.000Z","uid":316001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97e38d29cd661d4917237e7813fde81cea94b6b7","tid":1530770,"uid":316001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"話鳩佢蠢囉屌<br />\n叫得藍絲都係無乜腦<br />\n咁無乜腦嘅人不嬲都唔鍾意比人話蠢㗎啦<br />\n你要話佢之後最好加個'死'字<br />\n屌你正死蠢<br />\n咁依個方法最大嘅好處就係可以好無腦咁用<br />\n藍絲拒絕理性溝通<br />\n你咪唔好同佢溝通囉<br />\n正係話佢蠢<br />\n咁藍絲唔夠你講個陣佢就會話你比人洗腦呀<br />\n乜撚嘢啲示威者收左錢呀,乜柒咁嗰陣<br />\n你就話佢無腦,太撚蠢<br />\n吸收唔撚到正確嘅政治訊息,左耳入右耳出<br />\n教育程度又低,小學都唔知畢咗業未<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依個世界最蠢嘅人就係唔撚知自己有幾撚蠢</span></span><br />\n我依家就係教精你咪撚咁蠢<br />\n咁佢就自然會轉態"},{"pid":"4364f6530365d021e84f8c74493c68d735bd8356","tid":1530770,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"一早起身 不要說「早晨」, 試著說「人一藍,腦便殘」"},{"pid":"cf84413efff3dd35cc0cbfd5e3e588aa1f89302a","tid":1530770,"uid":316001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4364f6530365d021e84f8c74493c68d735bd8356","tid":1530770,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"一早起身 不要說「早晨」, 試著說「人一藍,腦便殘」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"ching好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3e9f2e2531baa254c44e5b78ae289a3e49d2da","tid":1530770,"uid":316001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb63ce7e949355faf5f361dba1f2fe652dc594d4","tid":1530770,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:15:28.000Z","msg":"TUITUITUI"}]}